Package: gdldata
Title: Global Data Lab R API
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Aaron", "van Geffen", , "aaron.vangeffen@ru.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The gdldata package allows users to retrieve datasets from the Global Data Lab
    website, straight into R dataframes. Functions are provided to reference the available
    options (indicators, regions, countries) as well.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    methods
Suggests:
    magrittr
URL: https://globaldatalab.org/, https://github.com/GlobalDataLab/R-data-api
BugReports: https://github.com/GlobalDataLab/R-data-api
